 de quelques l\u00e9muriens subfossiles malgaches|journal = Mammalia|year = 1938|volume = 2|pages = 57\u201380}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"1915Matthew\">{{Cite journal | last1 = Matthew | first1 = W. D. | doi = 10.1111/j.1749-6632.1914.tb55346.x | title = Climate and Evolution | journal = Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences | volume = 24 | issue = 1 | pages = 171\u2013318 | year = 1915 | pmid =  | pmc = | ref = harv|bibcode = 1914NYASA..24..171M | url = https://zenodo.org/record/1433318 }}</ref>\n\n<!-- News and web sources -->\n<ref name=\"Telegraph_19Aug13\">{{cite news|last1=Samuel |first1=H. |title=Furry lemurs 'could be wiped out within 20 years' |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/madagascar/10252191/Furry-lemurs-could-be-wiped-out-within-20-years.html |newspaper=The Telegraph |date=19 August 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130819174152/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/madagascar/10252191/Furry-lemurs-could-be-wiped-out-within-20-years.html |archivedate=19 August 2013 |url-status=live |accessdate=24 August 2013 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IBT_21Aug13\">{{cite news|last1=Mintz |first1=Z. |title=Lemurs face extinction in 20 years, risk of losing species ror 'first time in two centuries' |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/lemurs-face-extinction-20-years-risk-losing-species-first-time-two-centuries-1393907 |newspaper=International Business Times |date=21 August 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826134422/http://www.ibtimes.com/lemurs-face-extinction-20-years-risk-losing-species-first-time-two-centuries-1393907 |archivedate=26 August 2013 |url-status=live |accessdate=24 August 2013 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BBC_13Jul12\">{{cite news|last1=Black |first1=R. |title=Lemurs sliding towards extinction |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-18825901 |newspaper=BBC News |date=13 July 2012 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025103617/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-en